<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>三节课</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no,initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta content="yes" name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable"/>
    <meta content="black" name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style"/>
    <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection"/>
    <style type="text/css">
        html,body,dl,dt,dd,ul,ol,li,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,pre,form,input,p,blockquote,th,td{margin: 0;padding: 0;}
        fieldset, img{border: 0;}
        address, caption, cite, code, dfn, em, th, var{font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;}
        ol, ul{list-style: none;}
        a{text-decoration: none;color: #777;}
        a:hover{color: #333;cursor: pointer;}
        img{max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;}
        #wrapper{width:100%;height:100%;}
        #error{width: 480px;height: 230px;position: fixed;left: 50%;top: 50%;margin-left:-240px;margin-top:-115px;}
        #error .e-pic{width: 150px;height: 150px;float: left;}
        #error .e-con{width: 280px;float: right;}
        #error .e-con .e-title{font-size:50px;font-weight: bold;color: #f67280;margin-bottom: 10px;}
        #error .e-con .e-explain{font-size:18px;line-height: 30px;margin-bottom:5px;padding-bottom: 10px;color: #666;border-bottom:1px solid #DEDEDE;}
        #error .e-con .e-back{line-height: 30px;color: #666;}
        #error .e-con .e-back a{color: #9b9ee7;}
        #error .e-con .e-back a:hover{color: #8c8fda;cursor: pointer;}
        #error .error-foot{width:480px;float: left;line-height: 25px;text-align: center;color: #999;font-size:13px;margin-top: 30px;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrapper">
    <div id="error">
        <div class="e-pic"><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></div>
        <div class="e-con">
            <div class="e-title">404</div>
            <div class="e-explain">T_T 出错啦！抱歉，您访问的页面有错误</div>
            <div class="e-back">
                <a href="/">返回首页</a>
                或者
                <a href="javascript:history.go(-1);">返回上页</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="error-foot">
            2013-2016 &copy; 三节课 sanjieke.com All rights reserved.<br>联系我们:<a href="Mailto:kefu@sanjieke.com">kefu@sanjieke.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
